sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as regex-detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: PII/Regex Detection Request

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP, No Auth, No TLS
    Note right of Orchestrator: JSON Payload:<br/>- content: [text strings]<br/>- detectors: ["email", "ssn",<br/>"credit-card", or custom regex]

    activate Detector
    Note over Detector: 1. Parse JSON request
    Note over Detector: 2. For each detector:<br/>   - Built-in: compile hardcoded regex<br/>   - Custom: compile arbitrary regex string
    Note over Detector: 3. Run each compiled regex<br/>   against each content string
    Note over Detector: 4. Collect match positions,<br/>   matched text, detection type<br/>   ("pii" or "custom"),<br/>   confidence: 1.0
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>[[{start, end, word, detection_type, detection, score}]]
    deactivate Detector

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    Orchestrator->>Detector: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 "healthy"
